data.description: Nestled in the serene Smith Creek area, this charming cabin home offers a tranquil retreat near the Ochlockonee River ear the boat launch. With two bedrooms, full bath, a cozy living room, full length sunroom and screened porch our front. It's the perfect escape for a serene getaway. Outside, the property boasts a fenced yard, a deck for enjoying the outdoors, and valuable additions like a fish house, shed and an electric-equipped workshop for hobbies and projects. Situated on 0.28 acres in this beautiful natural setting, this home combines the allure of rustic living with modern comforts, making it a nice retreat. This is a must see before it is gone.
